name: Millone X
description: Good morning pretty one i hope you have had a good rest last night.AS i told you earlier,i truly want the opportunity to get to know you, all of you.I was raised by a strong catholic mom and being an only child she taught me so much about caring for people and accepting them as who they are .. respect,honor,dignity, honesty,compassion,and love.. were some of the strongest features that were instilled in me.I like to take things at their natural rhythm when it comes to relationships
